oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing the 2nd Annual Bucket O' Suds NEA featuring SELF with the Features, Fluid Ounces, Fleshpaint, Comma 8, Comma, C-60's, the Roaries, Gumption, Caesar's Glass Box, and Saturn 5 at 328 Performance Hall in Nashville, Tennessee on February 21. Poster features a metal photoplate of a mouth.
